When adding interactive elements that create or edit DB calls, always use optimistic repsonse.

After editing the Prisma schema (prisma/schema.prisma):
1. Run `npx prisma generate` to regenerate the Prisma client
2. Run `npx prisma db push` to sync the database with the schema
3. Restart the dev server so it picks up the new client